Project Name: TalentLevelUp

Description:
AI-Integrated Skill Development and Recruitment Platform

Tech Stack:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM
- JWT Authentication
- Zod Validation

Modules:
- Authentication
- Job Portal
- Assessment Engine
- Smart Ranking
- Analytics
- Leaderboard
- Smart Matching

Setup Instructions:
1. npm install
2. Setup .env
3. npx prisma migrate dev
4. npm run dev